<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/z?c111:H.R.801:">The Library of Congress (congress 111- Bill H.R.801</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110626121636/http://www.taxpayeraccess.org/issues/fcrwa/index.shtml">The Alliance for Taxpayer Access- issues</a></li>
